Case# SMPTETimeType.type5994Drop

iOS 2.0+iPadOS 2.0+macOS 10.5+tvOS 9.0+visionOS 1.0+watchOS 3.0+

```
case type5994Drop
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/CoreAudioTypes/SMPTETimeType/type5994Drop#Discussion)

59.94 video frames per second, with video-frame numbers adjusted to ensure that the timecode matches elapsed clock time.
